    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到异世界边境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏入一个充满日式幻想风格的开放世界生存冒险。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演被流放的公主莉泽洛特，探索超过 100 平方公里的边境之地，那里充满未知、危险与奇遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次旅程都独一无二，而你的选择将决定能否生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/f050f37e08627d93b2f8813ae8970bd5.poster.avif?t=1769437538\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/f050f37e08627d93b2f8813ae8970bd5.webm?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/f050f37e08627d93b2f8813ae8970bd5.mp4?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索充满生命与危险的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越森林、山脉、沙漠、草原、巨大迷宫，甚至魔界。收集资源，打造武器与装备，建造避难所以求生存。注意：怪物、幻想生物和野生动物构成了<strong>动态生态系统</strong>，考验你的策略与操作能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/4177d57ba739a3a2bc7fb0244f654e95.poster.avif?t=1769437538\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/4177d57ba739a3a2bc7fb0244f654e95.webm?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/4177d57ba739a3a2bc7fb0244f654e95.mp4?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike系统下的战略成长</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>怪物技能与卡牌：</strong> 击败怪物解锁技能，并获得<strong>强力卡牌</strong>。装备卡牌以增强能力，自由定制战斗风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>命运抉择：</strong> 每生存一天，可触发<strong>随机永久强化</strong>，包括额外卡槽、属性加成、大幅回复或稀有神器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡印记系统：</strong> 被怪物击杀后获得<strong>印记</strong>，在未来游玩中提供永久加成，让每一次死亡都成为成长的一部分。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/9bf6f5354c005e63f766f84a9c0a9156.poster.avif?t=1769437538\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/9bf6f5354c005e63f766f84a9c0a9156.webm?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332500/extras/9bf6f5354c005e63f766f84a9c0a9156.mp4?t=1769437538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造、制作、生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造属于自己的小屋，摆放床铺，收集食材并烹饪怪物肉以维持体力。学习不同流派的技能，打造独特武器，掌握新的战斗策略，为下一次冒险做好准备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生命与挑战交织的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史莱姆、熊、古树精灵以及无数其他生物自由游荡。探索、战斗、制作与策略布局——<strong>每一次冒险都由你的选择、战斗与生存决策塑造。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>联系 / 支持</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如遇BUG或有疑问，请联系：<strong><a href=\"mailto:lisslotte123@gmail.com\">lisslotte123@gmail.com</a></strong></p>",
